  <entry>
    <title>guide</title>
    <url>/2022/02/16/guide/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h1 id="关于hexo博客的搭建"><a href="#关于hexo博客的搭建" class="headerlink" title="关于hexo博客的搭建"></a>关于hexo博客的搭建</h1><h2 id="1-前置准备"><a href="#1-前置准备" class="headerlink" title="1.前置准备"></a>1.前置准备</h2><h3 id="1-1github"><a href="#1-1github" class="headerlink" title="1.1github"></a>1.1github</h3><blockquote>
<p>首先，需要自己注册一个<a href="https://github.com/">github</a>账号  </p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>然后，点击右上角的加号新建一个项目<code>New repository</code>  </p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>之后，在新建的选项里面，选择[^repository name]为<code>×××.github.io</code>，下面选择<code>Public</code>，然后<code>Create repository</code>  </p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>Check:显示<code>Quick Setup</code>等空白选项时表示成功  </p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="1-2git"><a href="#1-2git" class="headerlink" title="1.2git"></a>1.2<a href="https://gitforwindows.org/">git</a></h3><blockquote>
<p>点击下载安装git for windows(仅适用windows)  </p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>Check:打开cmd输入<code>git --version</code>若显示版本号即为成功  </p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="1-3node-js"><a href="#1-3node-js" class="headerlink" title="1.3node.js"></a>1.3<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/">node.js</a></h3><blockquote>
<p>点击选择左边LTS版本下载安装  </p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>Check:打开cmd输入<code>node -v</code>以及<code>npm -v</code>  </p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="1-4配置hexo"><a href="#1-4配置hexo" class="headerlink" title="1.4配置hexo"></a>1.4配置hexo</h3><blockquote>
<p>首先任选一个作为项目地址的位置新建文件夹作为<em>站点目录</em>，打开后右键选择<code>Git Bash Here</code>  </p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>输入<code>npm install -g hexo</code>，正常没问题，如果被墙又不能自行科学上网，就输入<code>npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</code>切换到淘宝镜像后输入<code>cnpm install -g hexo</code>  </p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>Check:输入<code>hexo -v</code>出现版本号即为成功  </p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="1-5自备-一个能写markdown文件的IDE-推荐用Microsoft配套的VSCode-，基本的VC框架-一般电脑都自带"><a href="#1-5自备-一个能写markdown文件的IDE-推荐用Microsoft配套的VSCode-，基本的VC框架-一般电脑都自带" class="headerlink" title="1.5自备:一个能写markdown文件的IDE(推荐用Microsoft配套的VSCode)，基本的VC框架(一般电脑都自带)"></a>1.5自备:一个能写markdown文件的IDE(推荐用Microsoft配套的VSCode)，基本的VC框架(一般电脑都自带)</h3><h2 id="2-基本配置"><a href="#2-基本配置" class="headerlink" title="2.基本配置"></a>2.基本配置</h2><h3 id="2-1初始化"><a href="#2-1初始化" class="headerlink" title="2.1初始化"></a>2.1初始化</h3><blockquote>
<p>同样在git中输入<code>hexo init</code>,等待安装后会出现: </p>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>node_modules:存放插件  </li>
<li>scaffolds:文章模板  </li>
<li>source:所有页面的markdown/html代码  </li>
<li>themes:下载的主题  </li>
<li>_config.yml:<em>站点配置文件</em></li>
<li>package.json:插件目录  </li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="2-2格式化"><a href="#2-2格式化" class="headerlink" title="2.2格式化"></a>2.2格式化</h3><blockquote>
<p>输入<code>npm intall</code>来下载一些基本包  </p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>下载完毕后，打开<em>站点配置文件</em>，在<code>site</code>部分:  </p>
<blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 博客标题  </span><br><span class="line">subtitle: 博客副标题  </span><br><span class="line">description: 博客描述（可以填写 xxx的博客）  </span><br><span class="line">author: 作者  </span><br><span class="line">language: 语言，稍后根据主题进行设置  </span><br><span class="line">timezone: 时区，不建议设置  </span><br><span class="line">```  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">配置后在*站点目录*下`Git Bash Here`输入`hexo s`或`hexo server`(没区别)  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">打开浏览器输入`localhost:4000`，可以看到一个经典Hexo博客  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">若端口冲突则`Ctrl C`后`hexo s -p 4001`切换到4001端口重复操作(之后的操作全部变为4001)  </span><br><span class="line">### 2.3主题挑选  </span><br><span class="line">[hexo](https://hexo.io/)中有着可以套用的众多[themes](https://hexo.io/themes/)  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">点击图片可以预览效果  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">点击蓝色字体可以查看配置说明，对照着配置即可  </span><br><span class="line">## 3.主题配置</span><br><span class="line">### 3.1准备</span><br><span class="line">首先在*站点配置文件*里更改`theme`选项为自己选择的选项  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">在git中用`git clone`或依照对应主题的`Readme`下载安装对应主题</span><br><span class="line">查看有无其他前置安装要求，有些主题为了框架完善使用更多插件</span><br><span class="line">### 3.2示例</span><br><span class="line">我使用的主题为`gal`，首先打开*站点配置文件*把`theme`值改为`gal`</span><br><span class="line">该主题前置要求的插件安装:  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">renderer:</span><br><span class="line">```  </span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-sass --save  </span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-scss --save  </span><br><span class="line">和之前一样如果被墙了就用cnpm  </span><br><span class="line">Or  </span><br><span class="line">yarn add hexo-renderer-sass  </span><br><span class="line">yarn add hexo-renderer-scss  </span><br><span class="line">```  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">json-content:  </span><br><span class="line">`npm install hexo-generator-json-content --save`或用`cpnm`  </span><br><span class="line">随后在*站点配置文件*中添加(或修改)  </span><br><span class="line">```  </span><br><span class="line">jsonContent:  </span><br><span class="line">  dateFormat: MM-DD  </span><br><span class="line">  pages:  </span><br><span class="line">    title: true  </span><br><span class="line">    text: true  </span><br><span class="line">    path: true  </span><br><span class="line">    date: true  </span><br><span class="line">    excerpt: true  </span><br><span class="line">    preview: true  </span><br><span class="line">  posts:  </span><br><span class="line">    title: true  </span><br><span class="line">    text: true  </span><br><span class="line">    path: true  </span><br><span class="line">    date: true  </span><br><span class="line">    excerpt: true  </span><br><span class="line">    tags: [&#123;  </span><br><span class="line">      name: tag.name,  </span><br><span class="line">      slug: tag.slug,  </span><br><span class="line">      permalink: tag.permalink  </span><br><span class="line">    &#125;]  </span><br><span class="line">    preview: true  </span><br><span class="line">```  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">然后准备备用页面搜索和404  </span><br><span class="line">```  </span><br><span class="line">hexo new page &quot;search&quot;  </span><br><span class="line">hexo new page &quot;404&quot;  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="4-自添加插件"><a href="#4-自添加插件" class="headerlink" title="4.自添加插件"></a>4.自添加插件</h2><blockquote>
<p>hexo所提供的插件功能<a href="https://hexo.io/plugins/">plugins</a>种类非常的多，这一部分为附加部分<br>这里参考一个<a href="https://www.pianshen.com/article/48331052709/">live2D</a>插件的添加，其他插件请自行按需添加</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="5-推送po文"><a href="#5-推送po文" class="headerlink" title="5.推送po文"></a>5.推送po文</h2><blockquote>
<p>blog的目的在于推送po文，我们有了github提供的免费地址，需要通过GitHub的ssh将本地传到互联网上  </p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>在<code>Git Bash</code>中输入<code>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &#123;email&#125;</code>，请把<code>&#123;email&#125;</code>替换为注册github所用的email，之后一路<code>enter</code>，就把ssh key存到电脑默认工作路径(一般为<code>C:/Users/Administrator/.ssh</code>)</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>打开该地址，找到一个<code>id_rsa.pub</code>文件，以记事本打开，复制内容，在github网站登陆后点击自己头像，点击settings在左边的<code>SSH and GPG keys</code>里点击<code>New SSH key</code>,将整个复制的内容粘贴  </p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>Check:在本地的<code>Git Bash</code>中输入<code>ssh -T git@github.com</code>,若提示<code>Hi &#123;username&#125;! You&#39;ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</code>则配置成功，并在<em>站点目录</em>中可以看到多了一个deploy文件夹</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>每次更新内容后发布:</p>
<blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo cl  \\clean旧的文件</span><br><span class="line">hexo g   \\依现有文件generate对应的网站文件</span><br><span class="line">hexo d   \\deploy到github网址</span><br><span class="line">(以上两行也可用hexo d -g)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Check:若发布成功，可以看到<code>INFO Deploy done: git</code>的提示，并且过一会打开网址能看到内容更新(有时需要等很久)</p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>写博客的细节过程可以参考<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/22498474">示例</a>  </p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>网上的教程参考<a href="https://lfkid.github.io/2016/11/16/Hexo%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%9A%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%88%9D%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C/">示例</a></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
